### Level 2 vs. Level 1: The Real Difference

**Scenario: You drive 50 miles per day**

| Level 1 | Level 2 (32A) |
|---------|---------------|
| 10 hours to recover daily driving | 2 hours to recover daily driving |
| No buffer for extra trips | Plenty of buffer for spontaneous driving |
| Stressed if you forget to plug in | Forgiving if you miss a night |

**Verdict:** For any BEV owner, Level 2 at home is a game-changer.

